text: The Courthouse of Tønsberg Tønsberg District Court is a district court located in Tønsberg, Norway. It covers the municipalities of Tønsberg, Andebu, Nøtterøy, Stokke and Tjøme and is subordinate Agder Court of Appeal.Tonsberg District Court ==References== == External links == *Official site Category:District courts of Norway Category:Organisations based in Tønsberg
